{"tid":1165490,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【魚蛋革命】黃台仰李東昇證實獲德國難民庇護","createTime":"2019-05-21T22:51:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T13:40:55.000Z","uid":33373,"like":70,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"962176d974d20aa7d81dde57c69d181c02b8617d","tid":1165490,"uid":33373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T22:51:56.000Z","msg":"據紐約時報報導，2016年農曆新年期間於旺角發生的警民衝突中被拘捕，其後被起訴及隨後棄保潛逃的黃台仰及李東昇，證實獲德國難民保護。<br />\n報導指引述黃台仰訪問指，「如果德國相信香港有司法獨立，就不會批准我們的難民庇護申請」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/s1cQMQ8/VJMedia-2019-05-22-3-30-12.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2Fs1cQMQ8%2FVJMedia-2019-05-22-3-30-12.png&h=ec359525&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n德國政府透過電郵回覆紐時記者，於上年批核兩名香港人難民庇護，但沒有透露姓名。"},{"pid":"4c057785e39bbc69a7837aa951d6c25443d4c998","tid":1165490,"uid":33373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T22:53:15.000Z","msg":"soure:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2019/05/22/194227/%e3%80%90%e9%ad%9a%e8%9b%8b%e9%9d%a9%e5%91%bd%e3%80%91%e9%bb%83%e5%8f%b0%e4%bb%b0%e6%9d%8e%e6%9d%b1%e6%98%87%e8%ad%89%e5%af%a6%e7%8d%b2%e5%be%b7%e5%9c%8b%e9%9b%a3%e6%b0%91%e5%ba%87%e8%ad%b7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Farticles%2F2019%2F05%2F22%2F194227%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%25ad%259a%25e8%259b%258b%25e9%259d%25a9%25e5%2591%25bd%25e3%2580%2591%25e9%25bb%2583%25e5%258f%25b0%25e4%25bb%25b0%25e6%259d%258e%25e6%259d%25b1%25e6%2598%2587%25e8%25ad%2589%25e5%25af%25a6%25e7%258d%25b2%25e5%25be%25b7%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259b%25a3%25e6%25b0%2591%25e5%25ba%2587%25e8%25ad%25b7&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6TTizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=21e560e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2019/05/22/194227/%e3%80%90%e9%ad%9a%e8%9b%8b%e9%9d%a9%e5%91%bd%e3%80%91%e9%bb%83%e5%8f%b0%e4%bb%b0%e6%9d%8e%e6%9d%b1%e6%98%87%e8%ad%89%e5%af%a6%e7%8d%b2%e5%be%b7%e5%9c%8b%e9%9b%a3%e6%b0%91%e5%ba%87%e8%ad%b7</a>"},{"pid":"b1ab5